sql:
SELECT AVG(credit_score)
FROM obligors
WHERE credit_score IS NOT NULL;

SELECT SUM(repossessed_proceeds_amount) AS total_repossession_proceeds
FROM repo_events
WHERE repossessed_proceeds_amount > 0;

SELECT DISTINCT loan_id 
FROM delinquency
WHERE current_delinquency_status = 1;

external_knowledge:
A payment is considered missed if its payment date is later than the reporting period ending date; 
A loan is considered delinquent if its current delinquency status is 1 and the reporting period ending date matches the most recent delinquency date;
A loan is considered zero balance if its zero balance effective date is not null and the reporting period ending date matches the most recent zero balance effective date;
A loan is considered current if its loan status code is 1; 
All other loans are considered default.
